      "content": "i know there's help out there, but it doesn't change the math. it's just numbers. every month we're deeper in the hole. i look at her and the kids and i just think about how much easier their lives would be if they didn't have to worry about me or pay for my mistakes. it feels like my existence is actually costing them their future.",
